<title>
<emphasis id="Harmonic_motion" effect="bold">

Harmonic motion

</emphasis>


</title>




<para id="p1028">
The kind of motion exhibited by a simple pendulum is often referred to as 
periodic motion in general, and simple harmonic motion in particular.

</para>





<para id="p1029">
Other devices that exhibit periodic motion may exhibit more complex harmonic 
motion. For example, 

<link id="a1047" target-id="Figure_2">

Figure 2

</link>

 illustrates a more complex form of harmonic 
motion. 

</para>






