<emphasis id="Good_result_with_only_five_terms" effect="bold">

Good result with only five terms

</emphasis>


</title>




<para id="p1085">
<link id="a1092" target-id="Figure_8">

Figure 8

</link>

 shows that only five terms are required to produce a fairly good 
approximation to a triangular waveform.

</para>





<para id="p1086">
A comparison of 

